text: The 16th District of the Iowa Senate is located in southern Iowa, and is currently composed of Polk County. ==Current elected officials== Nate Boulton is the senator currently representing the 16th District. The area of the 16th District contains two Iowa House of Representatives districts: *The 31st District (represented by Rick Olson) *The 32nd District (represented by Ruth Ann Gaines) The district is also located in Iowa's 3rd congressional district, which is represented by Cindy Axne. ==Past senators== The district has previously been represented by: *Dale Tieden, 1983-1992 *Lyle Zieman, 1993-2000 *Mark Zieman, 2001-2002 *Julie Hosch, 2003-2004 *Tom Hancock, 2005-2012 *Dick Dearden, 2013-2016 *Nate Boulton, 2017-present ==See also== *Iowa General Assembly *Iowa Senate ==References== 16
